                <h1>Mastercard Background Check Explained: What You Need to Know</h1>
                <p>When applying for a Mastercard, the issuer performs a thorough background check to assess your creditworthiness. This includes reviewing your credit history, income, and any outstanding debts. Maintaining a good credit score is crucial, as it influences your approval chances and terms. Be prepared to provide personal information and documentation.</p>
